Andres (1913b) reported a doubtful record of
H. pistaceus
from Egypt ( Alexandria ). The species is distributed in western Europe and North Africa ( Algeria , Morocco , and Tunisia ) (
Fikáček et al. 2015
). The presence of this species in Egypt needs confirmation.
